casebody.data:
No. 09-9869. Jerome Julius Brown, Petitioner v. Prince George’s County Police Department, et al. 560 U.S. 937, 130 S. Ct. 3359,

176 L. Ed. 2d 1243,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 4388. June 1, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 368 Fed. Appx. 147.
